stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> open : /issue-start &lt;id&gt;
    open --> in_progress : /issue-approve (stop-gate arms)
    in_progress --> in_progress : edits within allowed_files
    in_progress --> amended : /issue-amend (re-snapshot scope, clears receipts)
    amended --> in_progress
    in_progress --> verified : /issue-verify (all required_checks pass)
    verified --> reviewed : /issue-review (Codex native + adversarial)
    reviewed --> closed : /issue-closeout (every finding gets disposition)
    closed --> [*]

    note right of in_progress
        scope_hook enforces:
        - empty allowed_files = deny all
        - edits restricted to whitelist
        stop_gate fires up to 3 times
        before forced exhaustion.
    end note

    note right of reviewed
        Receipts required between
        approve and close:
        - verified
        - reviewed
        - findings_triaged
        Codex never edits.
        Claude is the sole editor.
    end note
